snippet.title: TMNT Arcade: Wrath of the Mutants - Official Console and PC Trailer
snippet.description:
Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Wrath of the Mutants, the 2017 arcade game by Raw Thrills based on the 2012 Nickelodeon TV series, is coming to all home consoles and PC on April 23. Developed by Cradle Games and Raw Thrills, it includes the voice actors from the show (Seth Green, Sean Astin, Rob Paulsen, Greg Cipes) reprising their roles as well as four-player local co-op.

#IGN #Gaming #TMNT
